### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5206/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Unauthorized access (no token)
GET http://localhost:5206/api/productlist
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid token
GET http://localhost:5206/api/productlist
Authorization: Bearer wrong-token
Accept: application/json

###

### Authorized access — full product list
GET http://localhost:5206/api/productlist
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token-123
Accept: application/json

###

### Authorized access — page 1, size 5
GET http://localhost:5206/api/productlist?page=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token-123
Accept: application/json

###

### Authorized access — page 2, size 3
GET http://localhost:5206/api/productlist?page=2&pageSize=3
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token-123
Accept: application/json

###

### Authorized access — search filter
GET http://localhost:5206/api/productlist?search=mouse
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token-123
Accept: application/json

